The wholesale price index rose 1.1 pctmonth-on-month in January 1987 after increasing by 0.3 pct inDecember 1986, the national statistics institute Istat said.    The index, base 1980 equals 100, registered 172.8 inJanuary compared with 170.9 in December.    The January 1987 figure represents a fall over January 1986of 1.7 pct after a year-on-year decrease in December 1986 of2.5 pct. REUTER&#3;